_METHOD_ tagged _PROTEIN_ protein is localized in the _LOCATION_ and promoter gus analysis showed that is expressed in the stele of roots and veins of leaves and flowers .
confocal imaging of _BLANKP_ _BLANKM_ fusion protein indicated that _PROTEIN_ is located in the _LOCATION_ .
